{"tid":254181,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 － 泡菜豬肉炒飯","createTime":"2017-05-23T04:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T15:20:19.000Z","uid":30742,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d94ea613793defeb95de0ce4c4e3f6caac7ca29","tid":254181,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/NXmHp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNXmHp.jpg&h=42393eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/t1xwkr1NnHA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ft1xwkr1NnHA&d=MIbL8IPx8DoPDBbnzfpd9f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b2ad3745\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/t1xwkr1NnHA</a><br />\n<br />\n之前有人問有咩係好簡單又可以做正餐的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外又可以帶埋飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得帶到飯而好食係要諗既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，無論蒸或者叮<br />\n隔夜餸好多都會變得難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炒飯係其中一樣我覺得隔左夜翻熱都唔會變既！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我自己有醃泡菜，又唔係成日食，變左老泡菜，即係比較酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得用黎炒飯同煮湯都幾好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炒個飯加隻煎蛋（重點！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），我諗真係無咩人會唔鍾意<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖文食譜: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/05/korean-pork-kimchi-fried-rice.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F05%2Fkorean-pork-kimchi-fried-rice.html&d=MIbL8IPx8DoPDBbnzfpd9f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d188545b\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/05/korean-pork-kimchi-fried-rice.html</a><br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=MIbL8IPx8DoPDBbnzfpd9f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=3cb5a015\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=MIbL8IPx8DoPDBbnzfpd9f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=bf725a62\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=MIbL8IPx8DoPDBbnzfpd9f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=49cdef54\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"a2d1d9d72e91072df44f9b99e9c5b6e93d0f3627","tid":254181,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:14:44.000Z","msg":"老娘係泡菜狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186df579eee8559d6fd367fde72df11db45b5d01","tid":254181,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似幾正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整啲想研究下risotto <br />\n老娘知唔知佢個隻risotto 係咪真係咁重要？<br />\n定普通米都差唔多"},{"pid":"5f9e03b1d21dcd064f780491931e0be5bd100129","tid":254181,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"韓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e3d1f25cb9605e5ff9e4f8ac64eebbc3fb5130","tid":254181,"uid":86377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:20:12.000Z","msg":"靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d4012f22681d3a304dd0b99c7fe596f8752bff","tid":254181,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:20:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老娘係泡菜狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n泡菜無咩問題～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我鍾意食酸嘛～又好食又唔肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3f53e811cb4bba080a89bc9cdd236f9f0da03a","tid":254181,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似幾正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整啲想研究下risotto <br />\n老娘知唔知佢個隻risotto 係咪真係咁重要？<br />\n定普通米都差唔多</blockquote><br />\n係有少少分別既～我分別用過珍珠米同risotto米<br />\nrisotto米係大粒d～無咁易淋晒～會煙韌d<br />\n但你話要我特登去買先整我又唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d0c8a992d1c215058cbdce84c9bca352f133fd","tid":254181,"uid":33796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:22:46.000Z","msg":"出面賣d泡菜有時好食有時唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea378f5160d1bd15f7ea4589d0b16aab3d68939","tid":254181,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c24248dbd518096b19ca30d6210d2e50a9ef47","tid":254181,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出面賣d泡菜有時好食有時唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得出面一定有加防腐劑同味精～因為要keep住放幾耐都唔變老泡菜<br />\n<br />\n自己醃都唔難啦！！不過個味一定無落左味精咁好食既～"},{"pid":"7e5321b572f6b47815254a2cc83e6282bdc91008","tid":254181,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:24:36.000Z","msg":"好食就得啦，我都鍾意用泡菜嚟送飯，唔係盲目崇韓無乜所謂，支持老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd85797b61a3ff79f7f72cf6f330af19075083b0","tid":254181,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>韓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n炒個飯ge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7133d3db22af2c86f8fc45548dcf5583695efd","tid":254181,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:26:19.000Z","msg":"泡菜真係韓狗唯一可取既食材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7661716b81fbf95ac5e36bc749d398572cf0b66","tid":254181,"uid":86377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:26:46.000Z","msg":"泡菜用大白菜醃?<br />\n<br />\n出面嗰d驚唔太衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c2ac5786b713c31c13fdddd252c21f